{"tid":2043940,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[31/5]  歐盟敦促美國重新考慮有關終止與世衛關係的決定","createTime":"2020-05-30T18:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T19:15:46.000Z","uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"320c432c235134747fe78f9c55268aa7a33a470e","tid":2043940,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T18:23:27.000Z","msg":"歐盟敦促美國重新考慮有關終止與世衛關係的決定<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529353-20200531.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529353-20200531.htm&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypDwxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=86a37e0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529353-20200531.htm&h=078d01ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529353-20200531.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n歐盟敦促美國重新考慮有關終止與世衛關係的決定。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟委員會主席馮德萊恩，以及與歐盟外交和安全政策高級代表博雷利發表聯合聲明，重申歐盟對世衛組織領導國際社會抗擊新型冠狀病毒疫情的支持。<br />\n<br />\n聲明表示，在全球持續抗擊新型肺炎大流行之際，各方主要任務是挽救生命，遏制和緩解疫情，而通過多邊努力團結合作，是戰勝疫情唯一有效和可行的途徑；世衛需要繼續領導國際社會，應對當前和未來的流行病，因此有迫切需要各方的參與和支持。聲明又表示，歐盟繼續支持世衛組織，已向世衛組織追加資金。"},{"pid":"de45bcef07b1f803c037bbc0e06fbfc087c28bda","tid":2043940,"uid":9067,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T18:24:25.000Z","msg":"侵：喂 喂  企開d啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"0e72bb3d6553b37babd1df0f46c0eedfc4be0c8b","tid":2043940,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T18:24:40.000Z","msg":"美國同歐盟決裂啦<br />\n<br />\n歐盟上下齊心奶共<br />\n<br />\n中國又成最大贏家"},{"pid":"067f5934a73746f08439e6f6ef7e3d0aa1669a46","tid":2043940,"uid":258592,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T18:25:43.000Z","msg":"歐盟成日想借中共搞9美國"},{"pid":"a7ca7bc988c70c440ff36d03126f987d39b6978d","tid":2043940,"uid":80724,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T18:29:50.000Z","msg":"叫你制裁又唔撚制，重要奶共，依家又叫人比錢重要最大條數<br />\n食撚屎啦垃圾歐盟"},{"pid":"22fccfeb52e6511c68baf55ec934d049ea2e1d74","tid":2043940,"uid":199957,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T19:04:03.000Z","msg":"歐盟唔想俾美國呢條最大嘅水魚走"},{"pid":"6e00f36cd905e4dc197add8cc29ecf5de5a362c9","tid":2043940,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T19:15:46.000Z","msg":"死歐豬你又想點呀"}]}